---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../globals.css";
import { Footer } from "../components/Footer";
import { Nav } from "../components/Nav";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Lobu"
  description="Lobu's privacy policy. We are committed to protecting your privacy and personal data."
>
  <div
    class="min-h-screen"
    style={{
      backgroundColor: "var(--color-page-bg)",
    }}
  >
    <Nav client:load currentPath={Astro.url.pathname} />
    <main class="relative z-[1] max-w-[48rem] mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <article>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm mb-12" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { year: "numeric", month: "long", day: "numeric" })}
        </p>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Introduction
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            Lobu is an open-source platform for deploying autonomous AI agents. We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about the data we collect and how we use it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Self-Hosted Deployment
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            When you self-host Lobu, you have full control over your data. All conversations, agent configurations, and associated data are stored on your own infrastructure. We do not have access to any data from self-hosted deployments.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Cloud Service
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            For our managed cloud service, we collect and process the following data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>Account Information:</strong> Email address and optional profile information you provide</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>Workspace Data:</strong> Agent configurations, conversation history, and connected platform credentials</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>Usage Data:</strong> API calls, message counts, and performance metrics for service monitoring and billing</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>Platform Credentials:</strong> Bot tokens and OAuth credentials for Slack, Telegram, and other platforms</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Data Sharing
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            We do not sell your data to third parties. Your data may be shared with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>AI Model Providers:</strong> Messages sent to AI providers (Anthropic, OpenAI, etc.) are processed according to their respective privacy policies</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>Service Providers:</strong> Infrastructure and analytics services that help us operate the platform</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Data Security
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption at rest and in transit, isolated worker environments, and regular security audits. Agent credentials are stored securely and never exposed to worker processes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Data Retention
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            Conversation history and workspace data are retained for the duration of your account. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us or using the account deletion feature.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Your Rights
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You may export your workspace data or close your account at any time from the application settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Cookies and Analytics
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            We use cookies and analytics tools to understand how our website is used and to improve our services. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect some functionality.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Children's Privacy
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            Our service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Changes to This Policy
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated through our website or via email for cloud service users.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text)" }}>
            Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed" style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}>
            For questions about this privacy policy or your personal data, contact us at:
          </p>
          <a
            href="mailto:hello@lobu.ai"
            class="text-sm underline"
            style={{ color: "var(--color-page-text-muted)" }}
          >
            hello@lobu.ai
          </a>
        </section>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
